{"tid":618890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七人車甩轆擊傷老婦","createTime":"2018-04-06T07:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T07:31:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"02d835c85a5aed7f5e9c0d2b78ba7b249b108588","tid":618890,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T07:31:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180406/20353623\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F20353623&d=UhcK7O4HZ2YeQOuwrYoL8i7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a576781e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F20353623&h=86286369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180406/20353623</a><br />\n<br />\n七人車甩轆擊傷老婦<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180406/large/06la6p21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180406%2Flarge%2F06la6p21.jpg&h=d2ebd5e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n婆婆被飛脫車轆撞跌。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】76歲朱婆婆，昨日下午2時許與家人行經黃大仙樂富邨對開時，遭一輛行駛中七人車甩脫彈上行人路的左尾轆擊傷，婆婆左手骨折、膝部擦傷及感覺背痛，當時她仍清醒並大叫︰「嘩！乜個車轆咁樣飛過嚟都有㗎！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尾轆飛彈40米<br />\n<br />\n肇事七人車司機姓黃（57歲），當時駕車沿聯合道往九龍城方向行駛，至樂富邨樂民樓對開時，司機報稱突然聽聞車底傳來嘭的一聲巨響，立即停車查看，發現左尾轆甩脫彈向行人路。據目擊者楊小姐稱，甩轆沿斜路飛彈逾40米後彈上行人路，擊中該名與家人同行的婆婆，婆婆被撞跌倒地上。楊小姐指婆婆後面有一群途人，若甩轆遲些彈出，或會有更多人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃祺文"}]}